This code accompanies the paper "Cyber Physical Games": https://arxiv.org/abs/2407.05817

Compilation instructions (requires the GNU Scientific Library)

gcc -o adversarial adversarial.c -lgsl -lgslcblas -lm
gcc -o collab collab.c -lgsl -lgslcblas -lm

